social_posts.post_text: i hope Rudolph eats the naughty list

happy birthday to my two best friends in the entire world🫶🏼 i am so lucky to have not only one but two people in this world that i can always count on to be in my corner or have a shoulder to cry on. i love you both with everything in my heart🤍 here’s to 24 years on earth!
note to self: always bring a hat
never met a sunset i didn’t like

Happy birthday to my beautiful momma🫶🏼 Thank you for showing me how to love and be loved, teaching me right from wrong, and most importantly never giving up on me❤️ Our tough times have made our relationship so much stronger. There will never be enough ways to show how grateful I am to have such an amazing women to call my mother. I love you🤍
She said yes, so I did too! 💍 I will forever be your biggest cheerleader but now I’m lucky enough to be your maid of honor as well🫶🏼 I love you future Mrs. Recinos❤️
i give you the world but there’s other planets too
a little party never killed nobody🥂 #2024
